To separate a region by the grid resolution follow these steps.

'''1.''' Select the part of the region you wish to edit 

'''2.''' Set the [[Pro_Tools:_Edit_modes#Grid|Grid Edit Mode]] to either [[Absolute_grid|absolute]] or [[Relative_grid|relative]] values.

'''3.''' Go to '''Edit > Separate Region > On Grid'''.





[[File:Pro Tools Edit menu separate regions on grid.png|275px]]




'''4.''' The dialog box that appears will ask you to specify a Pre-Separate amount (space at beginning of each cut).To separate exactly on the grid leave this set to 0.



'''5.''' Click '''OK'''




